{"type":"message","id":"45850033","parentId":"4e099ae3","timestamp":"2026-02-09T08:56:09.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"d76eae97-f962-4f09-9d8c-cf71c22e23c0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Daily Ping Configuration\n\n**Status:** Pending API configuration\n\n## Schedule\n- **Time:** 7:00 AM SGT (Singapore Time, GMT+8)\n- **Cron Expression:** `0 23 * * *` (11:00 PM UTC = 7:00 AM SGT next day)\n- **Delivery:** Telegram (@PC188)\n\n## Task Components\n\n### 1. GitHub Trending Repositories\n- **Source:** https://github.com/trending\n- **Count:** Top 5 repositories\n- **Blocker:** Page requires JavaScript, blocks scraping\n\n### 2. Bitcoin Price Monitor\n- **Source:** https://www.coinbase.com/en-sg/price/bitcoin\n- **Alert Trigger:** Price drop > 10%\n- **Blocker:** Cloudflare protection (403 error)\n\n## Solutions Required\n\n### Option A: Brave Search API\n```bash\nopenclaw configure --section web\n# Add BRAVE_API_KEY\n```\n\n### Option B: Alternative APIs\n- **Crypto:** CoinGecko API (free tier available)\n- **GitHub:** GitHub Search API (trending not officially supported)\n\n### Option C: Manual Mode\nUser requests daily summary manually\n\n## Implementation\n\n### Current Status\n- ✅ Shell script created: `/home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh`\n- ✅ Data sources working (CoinGecko API, GitHub API)\n- ⚠️ OpenClaw cron tool configuration pending\n\n### Manual Setup Required\n```bash\n# Add to system crontab for 7am SGT daily\ncrontab -e\n# Add: 0 23 * * * /home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh\n```\n\n### Data Sources\n- **Bitcoin:** CoinGecko API (free, no key required) — Primary\n- **GitHub:** GitHub Search API (top starred repos) — Primary\n- **Stocks:** Yahoo Finance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD) — Primary\n- **Backup/Fallback:** Brave Search API (configured, rate limited to 1 req/sec)\n\n### Rate Limits\n- **Brave Search Free Plan:** 1 request per second, 2000 queries/month\n- **CoinGecko:** 10-30 calls/minute on free tier\n- **GitHub API:** 60 requests/hour unauthenticated\n\n### Message Delivery\n- **Method:** HEARTBEAT.md trigger (not direct cron)\n- **Timing:** ~7:05 AM SGT (after data collection)\n- **Process:** Heartbeat checks log file → Formats message → Sends via Telegram\n- **Tracking:** `last-daily-ping-sent.txt` prevents duplicates\n\n### Note\nTrue \"trending\" repos require scraping GitHub's trending page (no official API). Current implementation shows most-starred repositories. Use Brave Search as fallback for additional context when needed.\n\n**Created:** 2026-02-02\n**Last Updated:** 2026-02-02\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1770627369550}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d58ce6f","parentId":"45850033","timestamp":"2026-02-09T08:56:09.567Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"dcadb4ea-48e2-4092-87a6-2db53f2da5c3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\n## S&P 500 Volatility Monitor (Every 30 Minutes)\n\n**When:** Every heartbeat (~30 minutes)\n\n**Command:**\n```bash\ncd /home/project/openclaw && uv run python spx_monitor.py\n```\n\n**Check Output:**\n- Parse for \"🔴 S&P 500 Status\" (drop detected)\n- Parse for \"🟢 S&P 500 Status\" (normal)\n- Check if change_percent ≤ -10.0%\n\n**If S&P 500 down ≥10%:**\n1. Extract: reference price, current price, change percentage\n2. Format URGENT alert message\n3. Send via Telegram immediately\n4. Log alert to `spx_alerts.log`\n\n**If normal (no alert):**\n- No message sent (silent monitoring)\n- Continue to next heartbeat\n\n---\n\n## Daily Ping Check (7:05 AM SGT)\n\n**When:** Every morning around 7:05 AM SGT (after cron job runs at 7:00 AM)\n\n**Check:** \n1. Look for today's log file: `/home/project/openclaw/logs/daily-ping-YYYY-MM-DD.log`\n2. Verify data was collected (Bitcoin, stocks, GitHub)\n3. Check if message was already sent today (check `last-daily-ping-sent.txt`)\n\n**If data exists and not yet sent:**\n1. Read Bitcoin price and 24h change from log\n2. Read stock data (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD)\n3. Format nice message with table and summary\n4. Send via Telegram to @PC188 (id:1087368827)\n5. Record send timestamp to `last-daily-ping-sent.txt`\n\n**Message format:**\n- Header with date\n- Bitcoin section with price and change\n- Stock table (6 tickers with prices and 24h %)\n- GitHub repos section\n- Market summary at bottom\n\n**Skip if:**\n- Log file doesn't exist (cron hasn't run yet)\n- Already sent today (check timestamp file)\n- It's not around 7am SGT (avoid duplicate sends)\n\n---\n\n## Alert Priority\n\n1. **S&P 500 ≥10% drop:** IMMEDIATE (send within 30 min)\n2. **Daily Ping:** Scheduled (7:05 AM SGT)\n3. **Bitcoin >10% drop:** Included in daily ping (not separate alert)\n\n---\n\n## Weekly Summary (Optional - Sundays)\n- Optional: Send weekly market recap\n- Include weekly % changes for stocks\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1770627369557}}
