{"type":"message","id":"2cee9b16","parentId":"b3dc21ea","timestamp":"2026-02-09T08:57:52.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've now recorded all the useful findings. Let me give the user a summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Done! I've scanned `/home/project/openclaw/` and recorded the findings.\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Project Folder Summary\n\n### Structure\n```\n/home/project/openclaw/\n├── skills/           # 5 custom skills\n├── logs/             # Daily ping logs (Feb 2-5)\n├── *.py              # SPX monitor, design extraction scripts\n├── *.sh              # Cron jobs, heartbeat scripts\n└── *.md              # Config & documentation\n```\n\n### Key Components\n\n| Component | Status | Purpose |\n|-----------|--------|---------|\n| **Daily Ping** | ✅ Active | 7:00 AM SGT — BTC + stocks + GitHub → Telegram |\n| **S&P 500 Monitor** | ✅ Active | Heartbeat every 30 min, alerts if ≥10% drop |\n| **Skills** | 5 installed | Design extraction, orchestration, finance, Slack |\n\n### Coding Agents Available\n- **OpenCode** → `/usr/bin/opencode`\n- **Kimi CLI** → `/home/pete/.local/bin/kimi-cli`  \n- **Gemini** → `/usr/bin/gemini`\n\n### Model Stack\n- **Primary**: Kimi K2.5 (via NVIDIA API)\n- **Fallbacks**: GPT-5.2, Claude Sonnet, Gemini 3 Flash, Grok 4\n\n---\n\n**Recorded to:**\n- `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-02-09.md`\n- Updated `TOOLS.md` with project skills and automations\n\nReady to work with this workspace. What would you like to do?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":4151,"output":384,"cacheRead":20672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25207,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770627454803}}
