-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/references/pipelines/rnaseq.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/references/pipelines/atacseq.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/references/installation.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/SKILL.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/scripts/config/pipelines/atacseq.yaml\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/scripts/config/pipelines/rnaseq.yaml\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/scripts/config/pipelines/sarek.yaml\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/scripts/config/genomes.yaml\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/skills/nextflow-development/LICENSE.txt\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/.mcp.json\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/CONNECTORS.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/README.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/commands/start.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/bio-research/.claude-plugin/plugin.json\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-support/skills/customer-research/SKILL.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-support/skills/ticket-triage/SKILL.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-support/skills/escalation/SKILL.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-support/skills/knowledge-management/SKILL.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-support/skills/response-drafting/SKILL.md\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-support/.mcp.json\n/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/customer-suppo